final_mermaid_code:
graph TB
    subgraph Client
        A1([New service]) --> B1[Enter the store]
        B1 --> C1[Look for a specific service]
        C1 --> D1{XORGateway}
        D1 -- Yes --> E1[Take his/her ticket representing his/her turn]
        E1 --> F1{XORGateway}
        F1 -- Physical --> G1[Client waits for his/her turn]
        F1 -- App --> H1[Choose the service]
        H1 --> I1([waiting time])
        I1 --> J1[Look for the product and specific criteria]
        J1 --> K1[Check how many tickets are ahead]
        G1 --> L1[Ask for a specific request]
        L1 -.-> M1[Register Request]
        D1 -- No --> N1([End])
        C1 -.-> O1{XORGateway}
        O1 -- No --> P1([Process Ended])
        O1 -- Yes --> Q1[Collects his/her order]
        H1 --> G1
        G1 --> L1
    end

    subgraph Request Assistant
        R1([Registering over]) --> M1[Register Request]
        M1 --> S1[Send the order request document]
        M1 --> W1([Register time])
        M1 --> V1([Shop assistants' team lose responsibility of this task])
    end

    subgraph Shop Assistants' Team
        X1([Preparation finished]) --> Y1[Deliver order]
        Y1 -.-> Q1[Collects his/her order]
        M1 -.-> Z1[Preparate order]
        Z1 -.-> Y1[Deliver order]
        Z1 -.-> AA1([Requires different specifications regarding the different services])
        AA1 --> AB1([Order description])
    end
